msgctxt "QL_Kakariko_Cha_001_Finish"
msgid ""
"Koko was panicking after forgetting to stock up\n"
"on swift carrots for the hasty veggie cream\n"
"soup. But now that she has the ingredients\n"
"she needs, there's a big smile on both Koko's\n"
"and Cottla's faces.\n"
"\n"
"　　\t<1.se_co>/////Koko's Recipe Corner/////<2.re_co>\n"
"One serving of hasty veggie cream soup:\n"
"\n"
"Add rock salt and fresh milk to a bowl of\n"
"swift carrots. Heat and stir to taste."
msgstr ""

